headline: Words With Friends Launches New Suite of Game Modes
summary: SAN MATEO, Calif., November 14, 2024--Zynga Inc., a wholly-owned publishing label of Take-Two Interactive Software, Inc. (NASDAQ: TTWO) and a global leader in interactive entertainment, today announced the next evolution of its beloved word game, Words With Friends, adding four new single-player game modes.
